  1217	### Deficiency Flow
  1218	
  1219	If incomplete:
  1220	
  1221	- User selects deficiency reasons.
  1222	- System generates deficiency / rejection communication.
  1223	- Application status becomes `Incomplete - Returned to Applicant` or `Rejected at Completeness`, depending on business decision.
  1224	- Borrower may resubmit after rectification.
